text: Teofila Băiaşu (born 25 July 1927) is a Romanian gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Romanian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Romania Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
